@startuml
title Class Diagram (Sequelize Model & Hardware)

package "Backend System" {
    class TrashEntry {
        + id: Integer <<PK, AutoIncrement>>
        + sensor_id: String(50)
        + count: Integer <<Default: 1>>
        + timestamp: Date
        + date: DateOnly
        + sensor_status: Text <<Default: 'active'>>
        + notes: Text
        + created_at: Date
        + updated_at: Date
        --
        + create(data)
        + findAll(options)
        + findAndCountAll(options)
    }

    class DatabaseConnection {
        - storage: String
        - dialect: String
        + authenticate()
        + sync()
    }
}

package "Hardware (IoT Device)" {
    class ESP32_Client {
        - sensorPin: int
        - wifiClient: WiFiClient
        + detectObject(): bool
        + sendPostRequest(sensor_id, count, notes)
    }
}

' Hubungan
DatabaseConnection "1" --> "*" TrashEntry : Mengelola Model >
ESP32_Client ..> TrashEntry : Mengirim Data Deteksi >

note right of TrashEntry
  Model data yang merepresentasikan
  entitas log riwayat deteksi sampah
  dalam basis data (SQLite).
end note

@enduml